idate啦）<br />\n第二：盡量寫d人人都明的工作／活動描述<br />\n第三：嘗試代入hr/manager身份去睇份cv，睇下cv可唔可以描述到你最獨特的特質／賣點，而且係fit到份工，咁先大機會突圍而出。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第三點唔認同, 我會寧願係interview 直接同manager 傾專門既野, 花時間整係cv度比HR睇隨時睇低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhr每個application都會吹到收幾百或者幾千封cv，點解要揀你個份？ <br />\ndetail野當然最好直接講，但首先要有interview"},{"pid":"dd57a9ca8d46f1b74c6a8d9e4f1c33738b959809","tid":241734,"uid":74279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T13:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>歡迎問題，會盡量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比資料你去賣？直接post 一個你認為最岩用既template出黎</blockquote><br />\n你delete哂個人資料就可以，講真，十份八份cv可以賣到幾錢丫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係我個人喜愛的template<br />\n<a href=\"https://1drv.ms/w/s!Akvqx6N_t2ABabMShraH2uACbtk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F1drv.ms%2Fw%2Fs%21Akvqx6N_t2ABabMShraH2uACbtk&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=26aad893\" target=\"_blank\">https://1drv.ms/w/s!Akvqx6N_t2ABabMShraH2uACbtk</a></blockquote><br />\n你呢個template 真係outdate 到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能啦，template呢家野好個人口味，同睇你報咩工。歡迎開心share update的template"},{"pid":"13f54e09ff2cd54dcc5a094f4bbdf85e67a930c5","tid":241734,"uid":43817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b22c5dda460ce7bb5902d1ed164ff085a050e89f","tid":241734,"uid":74279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>歡迎問題，會盡量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比資料你去賣？直接post 一個你認為最岩用既template出黎</blockquote><br />\n你delete哂個人資料就可以，講真，十份八份cv可以賣到幾錢丫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係我個人喜愛的template<br />\n<a